AUTH:
  All requests need header: X-API-Key = API_KEY env var

RISK GATE (checked on every signal request):
  1. equity <= 30 → max 1 position, 0.5% risk, 3% daily stop
  2. equity >  30 → max 2 positions, 1.0% risk, 5% daily stop
  3. consecutive losses >= 3 → cooldown (60 min, low tier)
  4. daily pnl% <= -stop_pct → block all new trades

SIGNAL FLOW:
  1. Check mode (ADVISOR → always NO_ACTION)
  2. Check symbol match
  3. Check risk gate
  4. Parse candles from query params
  5. Run strategy (playbook 1 first, then 2 if low confidence)
  6. Save signal to DB
  7. Return signal JSON

EVENT FLOW:
  On CLOSED event → update daily_stats realized_pnl
                  → update consecutive_losses counter
